Package: BuildSys
Type: Package
Title: System for building and debugging C/C++ dynamic libraries in R
Version: 1.0
Date: 2020-07-23
Author: Paavo Jumppanen
Maintainer: Paavo Jumppanen <paavo.jumppanen@csiro.au>
Description: A build system based on GNU make that creates and
    maintains (simply) makefiles in an R session and provides
    GUI debugging support through Microsoft Visual Code.
License: GPL-2
Imports: methods
